{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When present, this property takes precedence over "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textVariableAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "],"syntax":"json","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"top","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"left","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" anchor, ","type":"text"},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This property is only applied to the style if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" is non-"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"type":"text","text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". Otherwise, it is ignored."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Constant interleaved ","type":"text"},{"code":"MLNTextAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"CGVector","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" array values","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Predefined functions, including mathematical and string operators","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Conditional expressions","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Variable assignments and references to assigned variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Interpolation and step functions applied to the "},{"code":"$zoomLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" variable and\/or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"feature attributes"}]}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"textVariableAnchorOffset","symbolKind":"property"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/textvariableanchoroffset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"provide an array of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNSymbolStyleLayer/textVariableAnchorOffset":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset","abstract":[{"type":"text","te